&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1155&quot; data-local-id=&quot;f269faa97c7c&quot;&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Electrical Engineering, Aerospace Engineering, Mechanical Engineering, or related technical discipline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1283&quot; data-local-id=&quot;9dd667b39946&quot;&gt;2-3 years of professional experience in wire harness design, electrical systems design, or hands on harness manufacturing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1409&quot; data-local-id=&quot;5ea3e936f950&quot;&gt;Ability to read/interpret electrical schematics and mechanical layout drawings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1492&quot; data-local-id=&quot;dcd4363d365f&quot;&gt;Understanding of wire gauge selection, current carrying capacity, and voltage drop calculations.&lt;/p&gt;
