&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1592&quot; data-local-id=&quot;b9d867f39589&quot;&gt;Proficiency with 3D CAD software (NX, CATIA, SolidWorks, or similar) for harness design and routing.&lt;/p&gt;
