&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;This is a strategic and hands-on leadership role. The ideal candidate combines deep aerospace engineering judgment with strong product instincts, customer empathy, and the ability to lead high-performing teams. You should have&amp;nbsp;a strong sense&amp;nbsp;for what hypersonic test customers, defense customers, and advanced payload developers will want to fly — and how their payloads need to&amp;nbsp;interface&amp;nbsp;mechanically, electrically, thermally, and digitally with Arc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
