&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with engineers and other technical stakeholders to identify pain points, gather requirements, and translate loosely defined needs into practical internal products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow and strengthen best practices for internal application development, including testing, code quality, and maintainability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the evolution of the Internal Software Tools team’s products and technical approach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
