&lt;li&gt;Test high-performance accurate landing and recovery systems through aerial drop test campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualify designs through environmental testing, including vibration, shock, load, and thermal testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support prototype design, hands-on integration, fit checks, and issue resolution during build.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive design trades across performance, manufacturability, schedule, and cost.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with manufacturing, test, supply chain, and technician teams to bring designs from concept through fabrication and integration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with outside vendors and suppliers to source parts, review manufacturability, and accelerate development.&lt;/li&gt;
