&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain high-fidelity communication link budgets, modeling vehicle-level antenna radiation patterns and simulating RF performance in challenging flight and atmospheric reentry environments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&

